{"tid":872521,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"五角大樓證實兩艘美國軍艦例行駛經台灣海峽","createTime":"2018-10-22T18:06:27.000Z","updateTime":"2018-10-23T00:06:14.000Z","uid":79563,"like":15,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"c6cbc7d58cc85cdb080f923b3abbedde9b99a17b","tid":872521,"uid":79563,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-22T18:06:27.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"http://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1424263-20181023.htm\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1424263-20181023.htm&d=IaDdLTFpL6vYNUIIR22sNMPrXSGIZiPsBFv3mRhlVuk%3D&h=a57742b4\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1424263-20181023.htm&h=ad12308e\" target=\"_blank\">http://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1424263-20181023.htm</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://newsstatic.rthk.hk/images/mfile_1424263_1_20181023013848.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fnewsstatic.rthk.hk%2Fimages%2Fmfile_1424263_1_20181023013848.jpg&h=95eedc7e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n美國繼7月後，再派軍艦通過台灣海峽。五角大樓說，兩艘海軍軍艦駛經台海，沒有事故發生。<br />\n<br />\n發言人說，「威爾伯號」導彈驅逐艦和「安提耶坦號」導彈巡洋艦周一例行通過台海的國際水域。<br />\n<br />\n美軍太平洋艦隊說，這次穿越台海的行動展現美國對自由及開放印太地區的承諾，美國海軍將在國際法允許下，飛越及航經任何區域。"},{"pid":"e74d31c113245075de159ce1e9394f65e0a1775a","tid":872521,"uid":125193,"like":4,"dislike":1,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-22T18:13:34.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong>支那五毛狗 半年前說 美國軍艦例行駛經台灣海峽= 武統台灣??</strong></span>  <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/26.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/31.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/37.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: red;\">支那五毛狗 同我死出來</span></strong></span> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/33.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/as